  "about": {
    "label": "About Us",
    "title": "Built by Makers, for Makers.",
    "subtitle": "3DZAAP Print Manager is not just another tool — it's the mission to professionalize 3D printing worldwide.",
    "story_p1": "3DZAAP was built from scratch, thinking about the real challenges we face every day in the digital manufacturing universe. We know that managing a 3D printing business goes way beyond operating a machine — it's about controlling invisible costs, anticipating stockouts, professionalizing customer service, and, above all, turning hours of work into real profit.",
    "story_p2": "Our platform was born from the frustration with disorganized spreadsheets, \"by eye\" quotes, and filaments that run out at the worst moment. We decided to create the solution we always wanted to have: a complete, intuitive, and accessible system that puts the maker in total control of their business.",
    "val1_title": "Precision",
    "val1_desc": "Every calculation matters. Our cost engine considers power, wear, material, and risk — so you never charge below what is fair.",
    "val2_title": "Transparency",
    "val2_desc": "No hidden fees, no fine print. Your data is yours and our platform is open about what it charges and what it offers.",
    "val3_title": "Innovation",
    "val3_desc": "We evolve constantly with community feedback. Every feature is designed to solve real production problems."
  },
